    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I ran some tests this weekend and I found that the time is mostly spent inside the slider widget. After removing all slider widgets from the example, the time of render went from 15s to 0.5s and no crash anymore.\r\n\r\nThe time is mostly spent when computing snap points [`computeSnapPoints`](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/develop/src/components/Slider/Slider.js#L57).",
