    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For the `computeSnapPoints` (same for `computeDefaultPitPoints`) we should avoid to do it on every render. We can cache the results and trigger the computation from `willReceiveProps` only when the dependencies changed (`min`, `max`, `step`).",
    "created_at": "2018-02-05T16:50:08Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2662#issuecomment-363145497",
