  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I've continued investigating the issue here. It seems that one of the facet values `DynamicContrastRatio` has a range of [0 - 1000000]. I removed the widget that was using this facet and the 49 others widget behaved correctly. I also tried to remove the generation of snapPoints and it worked like a charm.\r\n\r\n@aviatrix you could use instantsearch.js and use another widget for the dynamic contrast ratio for the moment.\r\n\r\nOn our side, we should remove the snapPoints generation if `step` is not provided.",
    "created_at": "2018-02-08T09:46:26Z",
